- Sandbox/permission questions (why a path/command/domain is blocked, how to allow
  it): read `~/.claude/docs/sandbox.md` before spawning a lookup agent.
- Model/tier & subscription-limit questions (pins, subagent tiers, cross-model
  routing to Codex, why the codex plugin is off): read `~/.claude/docs/harness.md`
