- At task intake, if the work already looks top-model-grade (hardest long-horizon
  architecture/synthesis), say so before building up context so I can restart it
  in a fresh top-model session; never suggest `/model`-bumping a grown session —
  its whole context would then meter against the constrained top-model bucket.
